    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_"><anchor id="2DCAM-DIALOG-CAMLIFE"><keywords><keyword>2D-Cam dialog-box<keyword>Cam-Life tab</keyword></keyword></keywords></anchor><text styleclass="Heading2">2D-Cam dialog-box: Cam Life tab</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Table">To <text styleclass="VariableName">Calculate Cam Life</text>, you must : </para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">Parameters tab</para>
          <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#83;&#84;&#69;&#80;&#32;&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#58;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo STEP" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo STEP">Enable Show Roller and Cam Life </li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo STEP">Enter a safety factor (CAM)</li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="HowTo STEP"><text styleclass="SeeAlso">See</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-2DCam-ParametersTab" anchor="2DCAM-DIALOG-LIFETIME-PROPERTIES" styleclass="VariableName">Parameters tab &gt;</link><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-2DCam-ParametersTab" styleclass="Separator"> Enable Lifetimes, Edit Safety-Factor</link><text styleclass="Separator">&#32;</text>&#32;</para>
          <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">Cam Life tab</para>
          <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#83;&#84;&#69;&#80;&#32;&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#58;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo STEP" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo STEP">Enable / Disable “Allow Pitting to ~15% of the Cam Surface”</li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo STEP">Select a Steel Category, Heat-Treatment, and Steel Quality for the Cam</li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo STEP">Enter the Steel&apos;s Hardness as HV, HB, or HRC, within the Minimum and Maximum Hardness Limits</li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="HowTo STEP">Review the Lifetime Results</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">Cam Life tab</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text" style="text-indent:-36px; margin-left:39px;"><anchor id="2DCAM-DIALOG-CAMLIFEFACTORS"><keywords><keyword>2D-Cam dialog-box<keyword>Cam-Life-: Allow Pitting:?</keyword></keyword></keywords></anchor><image src="tog_plus.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_" figurelistinclude="0"></image><tab /><toggle type="dropdown" print-expanded="true" help-expanded="false" defaultstyle="false" src-collapsed="tog_plus.gif" src-expanded="tog_minus.gif" styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_"><caption><![CDATA[Pitting-Faktor einschalten]]></caption></toggle></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="2" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="MD-Dialog-2dCam-CamLifetab-CamLifeFactors.png" align="left" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"></para>
